snippet.title: Amber Heard ♕ Transformation From A Child To 32 Years OLD
snippet.description:
Amber Heard ♕ Transformation From A Child To 32 Years OLD

Music  :  Unknown Brain x Rival - Control (feat. Jex) [NCS Release]

Link  :  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bLZHcnuqscU

________________________

Amber Laura Heard is an American actress. She made her film debut in 2004 in the sports drama Friday Night Lights. After small roles in North Country and Alpha Dog, Heard played her first leading role in All the Boys Love Mandy Lane and appeared in The CW television show Hidden Palms. Wikipedia
Born: April 22, 1986 (age 32 years), Austin, Texas, United States
Height: 1.7 m
Spouse: Johnny Depp (m. 2015–2017)
TV shows: Criminal Minds, The Playboy Club, Hidden Palms, Overhaulin'
Partners: Tasya van Ree (2008–2012), Elon Musk (2016–2018)
